# CallDurationFilter

Filtering of calls based on the overall call length

**Properties**

| Name        | Type | Required | Description                         |
| :---------- | :--- | :------- | :---------------------------------- |
| min_seconds | int  | ❌       | Minimum duration of call in seconds |
| max_seconds | int  | ❌       | Maximum duration of call in seconds |
